node.text: Thank you to everyone who came out to celebrate my PLT collection! We really brought Jamaica to Los Angeles last night! 🇯🇲❤️🔥 Thank you to my friends @jackharlow @offsetyrn @dojacat @breerunway who performed and turned the spot up! Thank you @djsugashay @casanovaiam @zackbia for dj-ing and bring the vibes! @wifeoftheparty @umarkamani @acsimon y’all did the damn thing with this one!!!!! ❤️🙏🏽 🎥 @byjamiebruce

node.text: I’m literally crying right now 🥺😭 I couldn’t be in Toronto to celebrate the launch of my global @Puma campaign with my family so puma gave them a special day Downtown to see me up on the big screens. How beautiful is this 😭😍 seeing my mom and my grandparents so proud of their little girl is what really makes everything worth it. Thank you to my @pumasportstyle family for putting this all together and making my family feel so special! I know this is a moment they will never forget! ❤️🥰

node.title: London Fashion Week PON DEM HEADTOP 😍🤯❤️🇬🇧

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ♔Winnie Harlow♔ on August 29, 2021 tagging @shawellness. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: ✨🧖🏽‍♀️🧘🏽‍♀️ I’ve never taken a trip by myself for myself, or even been without someone I know for a long time. A few months ago I decided to to a leap out of my comfort zone and come to Spain for 2 weeks alone to a full body wellness retreat for stress management, healing, and to take care of myself mentally and physically. A reset. I’m so grateful for this new experience. I’ve made new friends, been introduced to new hobbies, had conversations with incredible people, tried new foods, and have learned more about myself. I’ve had time to read, work out, eat healing foods, detox, cry, and most important to me, process the millions of thoughts that run through my mind that I never have time to deal with. Remember to take care of yourself. Your mind & body are gifts without them you aren’t here ❤️ #MentalHealth @shawellness

node.text: I LOVE #SUNSCREEN 🧴❤️ the most IMPORTANT part of my beauty routine!
